        <title>Apache Incubator: Incubator PMC</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <section id='intro'>
            <title>The Incubator PMC</title>
            <toc/>
        </section>
        <section id="joining">
            <title>Joining the IPMC</title>
            <p>
                Joining the IPMC is just like any other PMC, once enough merit and community involvement is performed,
                PMC members will take notice and may vote on you to join.
            </p>
            <p>
                Foundation members may willingly join the IPMC at any time, to express desire send an email to
                <code>private.AT.incubator.apache.org</code>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="members">
            <title>Members</title>
            <p>
                A full list of IPMC members can be found at <a href="http://home.apache.org/phonebook.html?pmc=incubator">home.apache.org/phonebook.html?pmc=incubator</a>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="ipmc-roles">
            <title>Roles and Responsibilities of the IPMC</title>
            <p>
                The full list of expectations of an IPMC member can be found on the
                <a href="&root-path;/incubation/Roles_and_Responsibilities.html#Incubator+Project+Management+Committee+%28PMC%29">
                    Roles &amp; Responsibilities Page</a>
            </p>
        </section>
    </body>
